WeatherPredictionHMM/
│── data/                      # Dataset storage
│── models/                    # Trained HMM models
│── src/                        # Source code
│   │── preprocess.py           # Data Preprocessing (Pandas)
│   │── train_hmm.py            # Train Hidden Markov Model
│   │── predict.py              # Predict weather states
│   │── evaluate.py             # Model evaluation and comparison
│   │── visualize.py            # Plot weather trends
│── requirements.txt            # Dependencies
│── README.md                   # Documentation
